<h3><strong>How Does It Work?</strong></h3>
<h3>&nbsp;</h3>
<p>The Prepared Hero Fire Blanket works by suffocating the fire. When you place the blanket over flames, it blocks the oxygen supply, effectively extinguishing the fire in seconds. It&rsquo;s particularly effective for fires caused by grease, gas, or electrical mishaps.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Fire Suppression Mechanism</strong>: The blanket works by cutting off the oxygen supply to the fire, effectively smothering it. Simply place the blanket over the flames, and it will extinguish them within seconds.</p>
