<p><strong>Types of Fires It Can Handle:</strong> From grease fires in the kitchen to electrical fires, the Prepared Hero Fire Blanket is versatile. However, it&rsquo;s essential to know its limitations, as it&rsquo;s not suitable for large-scale fires.</p>
